---
import SectionLayout from '../../layouts/SectionLayout.astro';
---

<SectionLayout title="Why This New Site?" section="about" activePage="whynew" description="Why La Loingtaine created a new website — from music venue to cultural institute.">
  <h2>Why This New Site?</h2>

  <div class="content-centered">
    <p>
      La Loingtaine has evolved over the years from a <strong>music venue</strong>
      to something much broader — an <strong>"institute" for human development</strong>,
      inspired by Edgar Faure's seminal work <em>"Learning to Be"</em>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our previous website served us well, but it no longer reflected the full scope
      of what La Loingtaine has become. This new site better represents our expanded
      mission across four pillars:
    </p>

    <div class="pillars">
      <div class="pillar">
        <h3>Delight</h3>
        <p>Chamber music concerts that bring joy and inspiration</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar">
        <h3>Learning</h3>
        <p>Musical education that nurtures the whole artist</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar">
        <h3>Discovery</h3>
        <p>Scientific and intellectual exploration</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar">
        <h3>Sharing</h3>
        <p>Books, conferences, and cultural exchange</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>
      This new site also embraces modern web technologies for a faster, more accessible
      experience, while preserving the warm, artistic character that defines La Loingtaine.
    </p>
  </div>
</SectionLayout>

<style>
  .content-centered {
    max-width: 750px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .pillar {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-cream-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--color-burgundy);
    border-radius: 0 0 6px 6px;
  }

  .pillar h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .pillar p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pillars {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .pillars {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
